(48, 212, 105, 'For info on Nicoletta please click', '<p><span id="result_box" lang="en"><span title="Ik ben geboren in Itali&euml; en na mijn verhuizing naar Nederland toen ik 22 was heb ik lang met heel veel plezier als tolk/vertaalster gewerkt.">Nicoletta was born in Italy and after moving to the Netherlands when she was 22 she worked for a long time as an interpreter / translator.<br /><br /></span><span title="In 2000 begon ik met kookcursussen geven bij de Volksuniversiteit in Amstelveen.">In 2000 she began to give cooking classes at the Volksuniversiteit in Amstelveen. </span><span title="Het was een leuke hobby maar het smaakte naar meer, letterlijk en figuurlijk...">It was a nice hobby but she wanted to do more with it. </span><span title="La Cucina del Sole was het directe gevolgd van deze bezigheid: &eacute;&eacute;n van mijn passies - koken - werd op deze manier een beroep.">La Cucina del Sole was the direct consequence of this activity: one of her passions - cooking - became a real profession. </span><span title="Een regelrechte uit de hand gelopen hobby!">And she never regretted the career switch from translator to cooking teacher! </span><span title=":)">:)<br /><br /></span><span title="Vanuit een grote liefde voor de Italiaanse keuken en de beste wijnen heb ik mijn verdiept in technieke en originele recepten die binnen mijn familie van moeder op dochter zijn overgegaan.">Nicoletta''s great love for the Italian cuisine and the best wines brought her to deepen her knowledgde of the Italian cuisine further than what she had learned from her family. </span><span title="Ik heb mijn culinaire capaciteiten verfijnd met verschillende kookcursussen, een sommelier diploma en vooraal door ontelbare praktische experimenten.">She refined her culinary skills with some cooking master classes at Gambero Rosso in Rome, a sommelier diploma and innumerable practical experiments. </span><span title="Mijn grote culinaire passies zijn de klassieke Italiaanse keuken, de streekgebonden en historische recepten en de internationale keuken.">Her great culinary passions are the classic Italian cuisine as well as the regional and historic recipes, the healthy Italian cuisine and the international cuisine. </span></span><br /><span id="result_box" lang="en"><span title="Mijn grote culinaire passies zijn de klassieke Italiaanse keuken, de streekgebonden en historische recepten en de internationale keuken."><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: #000101;"><span style="font-family: Georgia;"><span style="line-height: 21px;">Nicoletta is considered a culinary </span></span></span><span style="color: #000101;"><span style="font-family: Georgia;"><span style="line-height: 21px;">expert and is often requested to give advice by the Consumentenbond, TV programmes like <a href="http://kassa.vara.nl/tv/afspeelpagina/fragment/test-pesto/speel/1/" target="_blank">Kassa! Pestotest</a> (Vara), "De smaakpolitie" (SBS6) and "Herrie in de keuken" (RTL4), radio programmes such as "Dichtbij Nederland" (Radio 5), newspapers and blogs (<a href="http://www.metronieuws.nl/nieuws/italiaanse-tv-kok-nicoletta-tavella-pasta-afspoelen-een-killer/SrZliA%21nAVsaeK6jVUT/" target="_blank">Metro article,&nbsp;</a><a href="http://www.parool.nl/parool/nl/5293/THUISETEN/article/detail/3337749/2012/10/27/Thuiseten-Koken-met-Nicoletta.dhtml" target="_blank">Parool article</a>, <a href="http://www.specialbite.com/blog/wat-eet-nicoletta-tavella" target="_blank">SpecialBite</a>, <a href="http://koken.blogo.nl/2008/01/15/recept-nicoletta-tavella/" target="_blank">Koken Blogo</a>, <a href="http://www.google.nl/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=46&amp;cad=rja&amp;ved=0CFsQFjAFOCg&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sjakes.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F06%2FNicoletta-Tavella-The-Native-Chef.pdf&amp;ei=UKHvUszcH-XJ0AW_v4GYCw&amp;usg=AFQjCNGeAIS8Jm7UYolQZkiCNEtokQOtPg&amp;sig2=2YZp72oCgnKfZZGGCAujUg" target="_blank">Sjakes.com</a> and so forth) and magazines (<a href="http://www.desmaakvanitalie.nl/eten-en-drinken-italie/chefkok-nicoletta-tavella-wint-prijs-voor-beste-italiaanse-kookboek/" target="_blank">De Smaak van Italie</a>).</span></span></span></span><br /></span></span><span id="result_box" lang="en"><span title="Ik schrijf over eten en wijn, oa voor mijn eigen culinaire weblogs: La Cucina del Sole (NL), The Sunny Kitchen (EN) en Cime di Rapa (IT/EN)."><span id="result_box" lang="en"><span class="hps">Nicoletta teaches</span> <span class="hps">classic</span>, regional and <span class="hps">healthy </span><span class="hps">Italian cuisine offering </span><span class="hps">single cookery </span><span class="hps">workshops</span>, <span class="hps">cooking courses </span><span class="hps">of several lessons</span>, <span class="hps">supperclub service,</span> <span class="hps">culinary advice</span>, <span class="hps">recipe </span></span></span></span><span id="result_box" lang="en"><span title="Ik schrijf over eten en wijn, oa voor mijn eigen culinaire weblogs: La Cucina del Sole (NL), The Sunny Kitchen (EN) en Cime di Rapa (IT/EN)."><span id="result_box" lang="en"><span class="hps"><span id="result_box" lang="en"><span title="Ik schrijf over eten en wijn, oa voor mijn eigen culinaire weblogs: La Cucina del Sole (NL), The Sunny Kitchen (EN) en Cime di Rapa (IT/EN)."><span id="result_box" lang="en"><span class="hps">writing</span></span></span></span>,</span> <span class="hps">presentation</span> <span class="hps">of</span> <span class="hps">cooking programs on</span> <span class="hps">TV</span> <span class="hps">and</span> <span class="hps">video</span>, <span class="hps">articles on</span> the <span class="hps">Italian cuisine</span> <span class="hps">and</span> <span class="hps">more</span>. </span>She also writes about food and wine for her own culinary blogs: <a href="http://cucinadelsole.typepad.com/" target="_blank">La Cucina del Sole</a> ( NL), <a href="http://cucinadelsole.typepad.com/the_sunny_kitchen/" target="_blank">The Sunny Kitchen</a> (EN) and <a href="http://cimedirapa.wordpress.com/" target="_blank">Cime di Rapa</a> (IT/EN).<br /><br /></span><span title="Mijn eerste koekbook ">Her first cookbook, "Antipasti" ISBN (9059205154), was published by Veltman publishers, and her second one, "<a href="http://www.cucinadicasamia.nl" target="_blank">Cucina di casa mia - Recipes of an Italian family</a>" released by Dutch publisher Choizes won the <strong>Third prize at the Gourmand Cookbook Award</strong> in Paris in the category <strong>"Best Italian Cookbook in the World"</strong> in 2013.<br /><br /></span><span title="In 2011 heb ik mijn eigen kookprogramma over de wereldkeuken gehad op de eerste en grootste Italiaanse foodchannel, ">In 2011 Nicoletta presented 40 episodes of "La cucina degli altri", a TV cooking show dedicated to the world cuisine on the first and largest Italian food channel, "Gambero Rosso Channel" (Sky can . 411 ). <br /></span></span></p>', 'ec18c0a96f3bd4d2e355421c48dde40d.jpg', '', '0000-00-00', 1, 0, 1, '2013-12-15 14:14:23'),
