(5, 205, '<h1 style="color: #b72025; font-size: 60px; font-family: Georgia1, Georgia, serif; font-weight: normal; line-height: 140%; text-align: center;">Vox Populi apologies</h1>\n<h2 style="color: #000102; font-size: 24px; font-family: Georgia1, Georgia, serif; font-weight: normal; line-height: 160%; text-align: center;">I am a dork and a cavewoman......&nbsp;SORRY&nbsp;</h2>', '2013-09-05 16:01:33'),
(6, 211, '<h1 style="color: #b72025; font-size: 60px; font-family: Georgia1, Georgia, serif; font-weight: normal; line-height: 140%; text-align: center;">Wie geeft er les? + Pers</h1>\n<p style="color: #000102; font-size: 15px; font-family: Georgia1, Georgia, serif; font-weight: normal; line-height: 160%;">La Cucina del Sole kan rekenen op een team <strong>ervaren Italiaanse koks</strong> en keukenassistenten die van je kookworkshops, teambuilding evenementen en kookcursussen een onvergetelijke ervaring maken.<br /><br /><strong>Nicoletta Tavella</strong> heeft La Cucina del Sole in 2002 gesticht en sindsdien is deze Italiaanse kookschool een begrip voor wie &eacute;cht Italiaans wil leren koken.<br /><br /></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 21px;">Fotografie: Jan Bartelsman&nbsp; - Visual Identity &amp; Web: Lemon Shuttle (Gaby Leon-van Wijk en Miljan Milic). <br />La Cucina del Sole (R) by Nicoletta Tavella 2002-2014</span></span></p>', '2013-09-06 02:40:44'),
(7, 212, '<h1 style="color: #b72025; font-size: 60px; font-family: Georgia1, Georgia, serif; font-weight: normal; line-height: 140%; text-align: center;">Teachers<br />&amp;<br />Articles on La Cucina del Sole</h1>\n<p style="color: #000102; font-size: 15px; font-family: Georgia1, Georgia, serif; font-weight: normal; line-height: 160%;">La Cucina del Sole can count on a team of <strong>expert Italian cooks </strong>and kitchen assistants who are going to make your cooking workshop, team building event and cooking course an unforgettable experience.<br /><br /><strong>Nicoletta Tavella</strong> founded La Cucina del Sole in 2002 and since then this Italian cooking school is an important reference for all those who want to learn how to cook the real Italian way in The Netherlands.<br /><br /></p>\n<p style="color: #000102; font-size: 15px; font-family: Georgia1, Georgia, serif; font-weight: normal; line-height: 160%;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="color: #000102; font-size: 15px; font-family: Georgia1, Georgia, serif; font-weight: normal; line-height: 160%;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 21px;">Photography: Jan Bartelsman&nbsp; - Visual Identity &amp; Web: Lemon Shuttle (Gaby Leon-van Wijk en Miljan Milic). <br />La Cucina del Sole (R) by Nicoletta Tavella 2002-2014</span></span></p>\n<h1 style="color: #b72025; font-size: 60px; font-family: Georgia1, Georgia, serif; font-weight: normal; line-height: 140%; text-align: center;">&nbsp;</h1>', '2013-12-15 05:01:00'),
(8, 221, '<h1 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 60px; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b72025; text-align: center;">Cursussen van 4 lessen</h1>\n<h2 style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 24px; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000102; text-align: center;">&nbsp;</h2>\n<h2 style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 24px; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000102; text-align: center;">Leer Italiaans koken con amore!</h2>\n<p style="padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: 25px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; text-align: justify;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Meerdere malen per jaar starten wij een nieuwe reeks van 4 Italiaanse kooklessen in onze kookstudio in Amsterdam Oud-Zuid. Iedere les bevat een selectie originele en smakelijke recepten die door de cursisten zelf worden bereid. Alles wat gemaakt is wordt daarna samen aan tafel genuttigd onder het genot van uitstekende Italiaanse wijnen. Het is ook mogelijk om een cursus of workshop in het Engels of in Nederlands/Engels te organiseren. </span></p>\n<p style="padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: 25px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; text-align: justify;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">De lessen worden gehouden op de dinsdag- of woensdagavond en beginnen om 18.30 u.</span></p>\n<p style="padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: 25px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; text-align: justify;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">La Cucina del Sole&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: ''Bookman Old Style'', serif; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: 17px; vertical-align: baseline;">&reg;</span>&nbsp;2002 - 2014</span></p>', '2013-12-15 13:53:33'),
(9, 222, '<h1 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 60px; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b72025; text-align: center;">Cooking courses - 4 lessons</h1>\n<h2 style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 24px; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000102; text-align: center;">&nbsp;</h2>\n<h2 style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 24px; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000102; text-align: center;">Learn how to cook Italian&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">con amore</span>!</h2>\n<p style="padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: 25px; vertical-align: baseline;">Several times a year we start a new series of 4 Italian cookery lessons in our cooking school in Amsterdam Oud-Zuid.<br />During each lesson you&rsquo;ll learn how to prepare a selection of original and tasty Italian dishes that we then will eat together, accompanied by excellent Italian wines.<br />The courses can be given in Dutch, English or in both languages for mixed groups.<br />The lessons are on&nbsp;<strong>Tuesday or Wednesday evening</strong>, 18.30 &ndash; 22.30 hrs.</p>', '2013-12-15 13:54:32');

