(76, 213, 106, 'Antipasti', '<h1 style="color: #b72025; font-size: 30px; font-family: Georgia1, Georgia, serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 160%;">Antipasti workshop</h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Antipasti - de Italiaanse tapas - eten is een van de leukste manieren om te lunchen of dineren omdat je de kans krijgt om nog meer gerechten te proeven dan tijdens een "gewone" maaltijd. Door de kleinere hoeveelheden raak je niet meteen vol en kun je nog meer smaaksensaties beleven.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Tijdens deze workshop gaan we verschillende gerechten bereiden, die kunnen varieren op basis van de beschikbare seizoensingredi&euml;nten. O.a. bereiden we een keuze uit deze gerechten: rotolini di carne con formaggio al tartufo (hamrolletjes met truffelroomkaas), polpette di ceci e prosciutto (gefrituurde balletjes van kikkererwten en ham),&nbsp;<strong>pomodori grigliati</strong>&nbsp;(gegrilde tomaten uit de oven), couscous siciliano con verdure (Siciliaanse couscous met groenten en saffraan),&nbsp;<strong>frittata alle erbe</strong>&nbsp;(een klassieke Italiaanse omelette met verse kruiden),&nbsp;<strong>tortini con zucchina e formaggio di capra</strong>&nbsp;(taartjes met gegrillde courgette, tomaat en geitenkaas), polpettine al sugo di pomodoro (vleesballetjes in tomatensaus),&nbsp;<strong>focaccia</strong>&nbsp;met rozemarijn,&nbsp;<strong>sardine alla napoletana</strong>&nbsp;(verse sardientjes uit de oven met knoflook, peterselie en broodkruim) en veel meer.&nbsp;<br />En natuurlijk gaan we daarna alles opeten met een paar glazen goede wijn erbij.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Data:&nbsp;</span></strong><strong>zaterdag 5 april 2014</strong><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Prijs:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&euro; 79,00 p.p.</span><br /></strong></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Tijd:</span>&nbsp;van&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">10.30 tot 14.30 uur</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia1, Georgia, serif; font-weight: normal; line-height: 140%;">&nbsp;</p>', 'dad3b543eded0ac461de1d1f7203b605.jpg', '', '05. 04. 2014', 1, 11, 3, '2013-09-06 02:50:19'),
(77, 214, 106, 'Antipasti', '<h1 style="margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 30px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b72025; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Antipasti workshop</h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Having&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">antipasti</span>&nbsp;&ndash; the Italians tapas &ndash; is one of the nicest ways to eat because you can taste more different dishes than during a &ldquo;normal&rdquo; meal. The smaller quantities are a plus: you don&rsquo;t get too full all at once and you can experience more taste sensations.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">We&rsquo;re making different little dishes that can vary according to seasonal ingredients. Among other things we prepare a choice of dishes among which (according to the season):&nbsp;<strong>tortini al caprino</strong>&nbsp;(puff pastry tartlets with goat cheese, cherry tomatoes and fresh herbs),&nbsp;<strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">rotolini di prosciutto con formaggio al tartufo</span></strong>&nbsp;(little cured meat rolls filled with a creamy truffle cheese),&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">melanzane ripiene al forno</span>&nbsp;(filled aubergines in the oven),&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">pur&ugrave;n con bagn&egrave;t verd</span>&nbsp;(roasted bell peppers with a tangy green sauce),&nbsp;<strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">frittata alle erbe</span></strong>&nbsp;(a classic Italian omelette with sweet onions and fresh herbs),&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">polpettine di ceci</span>&nbsp;(little fried chickpeas-ham balls),&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">rotolini di melanzane gratinate</span>&nbsp;(rolls made of grilled aubergines filled with pecorino cheese and herbs),&nbsp;<strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">polpettine al sugo</span></strong>&nbsp;(meatballs in tomato sauce),&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">sarde imbottite alla siciliana</span>&nbsp;(fresh sardines in the oven with raisins, pine nuts, parsley and bread crumbs) and much more. Of course after cooking we&rsquo;ll eat everything we made accompanied by a couple of glasses of good Italian wine!</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Dates:&nbsp;</span></strong><strong>Saturday 5 April 2014</strong><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Price:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&euro; 79,00 p.p.</span><br /></strong></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Time:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">10.30 to 14.30&nbsp;</span></strong></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">hrs</span></strong></span></span></strong></span></p>', 'dad3b543eded0ac461de1d1f7203b605.jpg', '', '05. 04. 2014.', 1, 8, 0, '2013-09-06 02:50:19'),
(78, 213, 106, 'De perfecte risotto maken', '<h1 style="color: #b72025; font-size: 30px; font-family: Georgia1, Georgia, serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 160%;">De perfecte risotto maken</h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">"Risotto maken is moeilijk" en "Het duurt altijd drie kwartier-een uur voordat het klaar is" horen we vaak op onze kookworkshops. Niets is minder waar want een perfecte risotto is zo gepiept. Je hebt weliswaar enig geduld (maximaal zo''n twintig minuten) en goede ingredi&euml;nten nodig, dat wel. En met de kennis die je tijdens deze workshop kunt opdoen zul je in staat zijn om je fantasie de vrije loop te geven en allerlei fantastische, romige risotto''s te maken.</span></p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Tijdens deze workshop gaan we 4 verschillende gerechten bereiden: een&nbsp;<strong>risotto alla milanese con ossobuco (</strong>heerlijke saffraanrisotto met in een rijke saus gesmoorde kalfsschenkel), de&nbsp;<strong>risotto ai frutti di mare</strong>&nbsp;(risotto met vis - zelf gefileerd en schoongemaakt -venusschelpjes en verse kruiden), een <strong>zwarte risotto</strong>&nbsp;en de vrolijke&nbsp;<strong>risotto con verdure di stagione</strong>&nbsp;(met seizoensgroente en kaas) in het voorjaar of de zalige&nbsp;<strong>risotto con zucca e funghi porcini</strong>&nbsp;(met pompoen en eekhorntjesbrood) in de koudere wintermaanden. Ook zullen we een lichte gemengde salade maken en lekkere peren gevuld met ricotta en chocolade of ricotta bekertjes met in wijn gepocheerd fruit als dessert.</span></p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Je krijgt ook tips om andere ingredi&euml;nten en methodes (soorten rijst, wel of geen stoompan enz.) te gebruiken om <em>il risotto perfetto</em> te maken zodat je je familie en gasten kunt verrassen met dit klassiek Noord-Italiaans gerecht in allerlei fantastische combinaties.</span></p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Data:&nbsp;</span><span class="datetext" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">zondag 30 maart 2014, zondag 16 november 2014</span> </strong><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Prijs:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&euro; 79,00 p.p.</span></strong></span><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Tijd:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">16.30 t/m 21.30 uur</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Om in te schrijven stuur ajb een mailtje via de "<a href="../../contact" target="_blank">Contact</a>" pagina.</span></strong></span></p>', 'a7fdf01353f823a7aa17ad14cb07acb3.jpg', '', '30. 03. 2014', 1, 9, 0, '2013-09-06 02:59:21'),
(79, 214, 106, 'Risotto', '<h1 style="margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 30px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b72025; background-color: #fbaa3e;">The perfect Risotto workshop</h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&ldquo;Making risotto is difficult&rdquo; and &ldquo;It always takes 45 minutes &ndash; an hour before it&rsquo;s ready&rdquo; are complaints we often hear about risotto. Actually,&nbsp;<strong>making the perfect risotto can be easy, fast and very, very rewarding</strong>&nbsp;if you know how to do it. Some patience, the best ingredients and our tips will help you do that. After this workshop you&rsquo;ll be able to make fantastic creamy risottos in lots of different variations!</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">We make 4 dishes:&nbsp;<strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">risotto alla milanese con ossobuco</span></strong>&nbsp;(saffron risotto with braised veal shank),<strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">risotto ai frutti di mare</span></strong>&nbsp;(with fish &ndash; you also learn how to fillet it! &ndash; cockles, shrimp and herbs), a<strong>black risotto</strong>&nbsp;and the&nbsp;<strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">risotto con verdure di stagione&nbsp;</span></strong>(with vegetables and cheese) in Spring/Summer or the wonderful&nbsp;<strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">risotto con zucca e funghi porcini</span></strong>&nbsp;(with pumpkin and porcini mushrooms) during Autum/Winter. A good salad as a side dish and pears filled with ricotta and chocolate as dessert will make this workshop complete.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">You also get tips on using other ingredients and cooking methods (types of rice, pressure cooker yes or no etc) to make&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">il risotto perfetto</span>&nbsp;so that you can surprise friends and family with this classic Norther Italian dish in all sorts of fantastic combinations.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Dates:&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span class="datetext" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Sunday 30 March 2014</span>&nbsp;</strong><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Price:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&euro; 79,00 p.p.</span></strong></span><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Time:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">16.30 to 21.30 hrs</span></strong></span></p>', 'a7fdf01353f823a7aa17ad14cb07acb3.jpg', '', '30. 03. 2014.', 1, 10, 0, '2013-09-06 02:59:21'),
(80, 213, 106, 'Sicilia', '<h1 style="color: #b72025; font-size: 30px; font-family: Georgia1, Georgia, serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 160%;">De Siciliaanse keuken</h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Tijdens deze workshop gaan we kennismaken met de heerlijke recepten uit Sicili&euml;, die in de loop der eeuwen een echte smeltkroes van verschillende volkeren is geweest (Fenici&euml;rs, Grieken, Noormannen, Arabieren, Spanjaarden, Fransen...) en het beste uit al deze keukens heeft weten te combineren in heerlijke, zonnige gerechten.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">We gaan&nbsp;<strong>arancini di riso</strong>&nbsp;maken, gefrituurde rijstballetjes gevuld met doperwtjes en mozzarella, en daarna twee geweldige gerechten: de&nbsp;<strong>pollo alla cacciatora</strong>&nbsp;(kip gestoofd in rode wijn met groenten, olijven en kappertjes) en de&nbsp;<strong>caponata</strong>&nbsp;(een paprika-aubergine stoofschotel) met krokante crostini, samen met heerlijke&nbsp;<strong>gevulde tomaten uit de oven</strong>. Als dessert maken we de beroemde&nbsp;<strong>cassata siciliana</strong>&nbsp;(rijkgevulde taart met ricottakaas, gekonfijte sinaasappelschilletjes en chocolade). Tijdens het diner zullen we krachtige Siciliaanse wijnen vol zon drinken en de avond zal worden afgesloten met een glaasje Marsala (likeurwijn) bij het dessert en natuurlijk een kop koffie of thee.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Data: </span>zondag 13 april 2014</strong></span>, <strong>zondag 1 juni 2014, donderdag 16 oktober 2014</strong><br /><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Prijs:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&euro; 79,00 p.p.</span>&nbsp;<br /></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Tijden:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">op donderdag: 18.30 t/m 22.30 uur,</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">op zondag: 16.30 uur t/m 21.30 uur.<br /></span></span></strong></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Om in te schrijven stuur ajb een mailtje via de "<a href="../../contact" target="_blank">Contact</a>" pagina.</span></strong></span></p>', 'e8aef39001dbbd79805396d5b3d139f7.jpg', '', '13. 04. 2014.', 1, 1, 2, '2013-09-06 03:05:25'),
(81, 214, 106, 'Sicilia', '<h1 style="margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 30px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b72025; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Sicilian menu</h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">We&rsquo;re cooking wonderful recipes from Sicily, a region that has been influenced by many cultures&nbsp; (Phoenician, Greek, Norman, Arabic, Spanish, French&hellip;) and has combined all these influences in wonderful, sun-filled dishes.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">We&rsquo;re making&nbsp;<strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">arancini di riso</span></strong>, fried rice balls filled with meat and mozzarella, then&nbsp;<strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">pollo alla cacciatora</span></strong>&nbsp;(a great chicken stew with red wine, vegetables, olives and capers) and&nbsp;<strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">caponata</span></strong>&nbsp;(a vegetable stew with bell peppers and aubergines) with crunchy&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">crostini</span>,&nbsp;<strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">pomodori ripieni&nbsp;</span></strong>(stuffed, oven-baked tomatoes) and the famous&nbsp;<strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">cassata</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">siciliana</span></strong>&nbsp;(a rich cake filled with ricotta cheese, candied orange peels and chocolate). During our meal we&rsquo;ll drink wonderful full-bodied Sicilian wines and we&rsquo;ll end this culinary experience with a glass of&nbsp;<strong>Marsala (</strong>liqueur wine) with our dessert plus, of course, a cup of coffee or tea.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Dates:&nbsp;</span></strong><strong>&nbsp;Sunday 13 April 2014, </strong><strong>Sunday 1 June 2014, Thursday 16 October 2014</strong><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Price:</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;&euro; 79,00 p.p.</span></strong>&nbsp;<br /></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Times:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">on&nbsp;</span></strong></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span class="datetext" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span class="datetext" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Sundays&nbsp;</span></strong>16.30 - 21.00 hrs, on Tuesday and Thursdays 18.30 - 22.30 hrs<br /></span></strong></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><br />To enroll please send an email using the "<a href="../../contact" target="_blank">Contact</a>" page.</span></strong></span></p>', 'e8aef39001dbbd79805396d5b3d139f7.jpg', '', '16. 02. 2014.', 1, 1, 1, '2013-09-06 03:05:25'),
(96, 213, 106, 'Pasta', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style="margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 30px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b72025; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Pasta workshop</h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Hoofdthema van deze kookworkshop is de zelfgemaakte verse pasta. Alles wat je altijd had willen weten over pasta met de tips en trucs van onze ervaren pastadeskundigen. Tijdens deze workshop kun je echt al je vragen over pasta kwijt.&nbsp;<br />We gaan&nbsp;<strong>vijf verschillende pastasoorten</strong>&nbsp;maken:&nbsp;<strong>ravioli</strong>&nbsp;gevuld met ricotta en spinazie, <strong>maltagliati</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>corzetti</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>spaghetti alla chitarra</strong>&nbsp;en&nbsp;<strong>tagliatelle</strong>. Alles natuurlijk met de bijbehorende sauzen waaronder de klassieke "<em>burro e salvia</em>" (boter en salie) voor de ravioli, de&nbsp;<strong>pesto alla genovese</strong>voor de corzetti - familierecept van Nicoletta die net als de pesto in Genua geboren is! - en de heerlijke <strong>tomaten-basilicumsaus</strong>&nbsp;met een vleugje knoflook, de <em>sugo di pomodoro classico</em> die alle Italianen minstens een paar keer per week eten.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Iedereen gaat oefenen met het maken van het perfecte pastadeeg en het werken met een pastamachine (tijdens de workshop is het ook mogelijk om een&nbsp;<strong>Imperia</strong>&nbsp;pastamachine aan te schaffen, zie "<strong>Dranken, Cadeaubonnen en Pastamachine</strong>" onder "Prijzen").&nbsp;<br />Alle pastagerechten worden daarna samen aan tafel geproefd en ge&euml;valueerd en natuurlijk drinken we een glaasje wijn erbij. Een lekkere fruitsalade met munt en specerijen als dessert en een kopje koffie of thee zijn de perfecte afsluiter van deze kookworkshop.</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><br /><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Data: </span></strong><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">zaterdag 22 maart 2014, zondag 25 mei</strong><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&nbsp;2014</strong><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong>Prijs:&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&euro; 79,00 p.p.</span></strong>&nbsp;<br /></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong>Tijden:&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">op zaterdag 10.30 - 14.30 uur, op zondag 16.30 - 21.30 uu</span></strong></span><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; background-color: #fbaa3e; color: #000101;">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Om in te schrijven stuur ajb een mailtje via de "<a href="../../contact" target="_blank">Contact</a>" pagina.</span></strong></span></p>', '52a27f7198d282bd31944fad4453368d.jpg', '', '22. 03. 2014.', 1, 0, 1, '2013-12-07 13:16:12'),
(97, 214, 106, 'Pasta', '<h1 style="margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 30px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b72025; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Pasta workshop</h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong>Homemade pasta</strong>&nbsp;is the main theme. Everything you always wanted to know about pasta, with tips and tricks from our Italian cooks. During this workshop you can ask everything you never dared to. As long as it&rsquo;s about pasta. ;)<br /></span></p>\n<p class="Standaard-P" style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">We&rsquo;re making 5 different types of pasta with sauces:&nbsp;</span><strong><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">ravioli</span></strong><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;filled with ricotta and spinach in butter and sage sauce, stamp-shaped corzetti with&nbsp;<strong>pesto</strong>&nbsp;(Nicoletta was born in &ldquo;pesto city&rdquo; Genova and this is her family recipe) plus classic&nbsp;</span><strong><span class="Standaard-C7" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">tagliatelle</span></strong><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;with an even more&nbsp;<strong>classic tomato-basil sauce</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>spaghetti alla chitarra</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>maltagliati</strong>.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />Everybody is going to make&nbsp;<strong>perfect pasta dough</strong>&nbsp;and is going to work with a pasta machine (we also sell Imperia pasta machines, the very best ones, see "Possibilities"</span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">). After cooking we eat and evaluate together our pastas/sauces while drinking some good Italian wines. A nice fruit salad with spices and whipped cream plus a cup of coffee or tea are the perfect&nbsp;</span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">way to end this cooking workshop</span></p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Dates:</span></strong>&nbsp;<strong>Sunday 2 February 2014 FULL,</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Saturday 22 March 2014, Sunday 25 May 2014</strong><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong>Price:&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&euro; 79,00 p.p.</span></strong>&nbsp;<br /></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong>Time:&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">on Tuesdays 18.30 - 22.30 hrs, Saturdays 10.30 - 14.30 hrs, on Sundays 16.30 - 21.30 hrs<br /></span></strong></span><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">To enroll please send an email using the "<a href="../../contact" target="_blank">Contact</a>" page.</span></strong></span></p>', '52a27f7198d282bd31944fad4453368d.jpg', '', '22. 03. 2014.', 1, 0, 1, '2013-12-07 13:16:12'),
(99, 213, 106, 'Toscana', '<h1 style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia1, Georgia, serif; font-size: 30px; line-height: 160%; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b72025; background-color: #fbaa3e; font-weight: bold;">Toscaanse keuken</h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Zeg het woord "Toscaans" en iedereen glimlacht. De Toscaanse keuken is ontzettend geliefd. Dat is natuurlijk helemaal begrijpelijk gezien het feit dat deze keuken een perfecte combinatie van simpelheid, puurheid en intensiteit vertoont.&nbsp;<br /><strong>Voor de workshop TOSCANE 1</strong> beginnen met de <em>crostini toscani</em>, twee soorten krokante crostini, dan gaan we verder met de <em>pici briciolati</em>, zelfgemaakte dikke spaghetti met knoflook en pepertjes. Als hoofdgerecht hebben we de <em>scottiglia</em>, een heerlijke stoofschotel in tomatensaus met verschillende soorten vlees en twee mooie bijgerechten. Deze maaltijd wordt afgesloten met twee zoete specialiteiten, de <em>ricciarelli</em> uit Siena en de <em>cantuccini</em> uit Prato (amandelkoekjes die we dan in vinsanto - d&eacute; Toscaanse likeurwijn - dopen).<br /><br /><strong>Voor de workshop TOSCANE 2</strong> maken we o.a. <em>crostini di caccia toscani </em>(crostini met kippenlevertjespat&eacute;)<em>, testaroli al pesto etrusco</em> (handgemaakte testaroli pasta met Etruskische pesto), <em>peposo </em>(rijke stoofschotel van rundvlees met groente, rode wijn en veel zwarte peper), <em>funghi in umido alla toscana</em> (gestoofde paddenstoelen) en <em>torta della nonna</em> (taart met custard en pijnboompitten).</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Alle gerechten worden uiteraard begeleid door uitstekende Toscaanse wijnen.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; font-family: Georgia1,Georgia,serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 140%; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; background-color: #fbaa3e; font-weight: normal;"><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Data TOSCANE 1: </span></strong><strong>donderdag 3 april 2014, donderdag 18 september 2014, zondag 2 november 2014</strong><br /><span style="font-size: 15px;"><strong><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Data TOSCANE 2:&nbsp;</span></strong></strong> <span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>nog nader te bepalen<br /></strong></span></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Prijs:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&euro; 79,00 p.p.</span><br /></strong></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Tijden:</span> <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">op donderdag 18.30 t/m 22.30 uur, op zondag 16.30 t/m 21.00 uur<br /></span></strong></span><br /><span class="datetext" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Om in te schrijven stuur ajb een mailtje via de "<a href="../../contact" target="_blank">Contact</a>" pagina.</span></p>', '4d10947e26e7be83f20ea1b2e361ae4b.jpg', '', '03. 04. 2014.', 1, 4, 1, '2013-12-07 13:32:41');
