(100, 214, 106, 'Toscana', '<h1 style="margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 30px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b72025; background-color: #fbaa3e;">The Tuscan cuisine</h1>\n<p class="Standaard-P" style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Say the word &ldquo;Tuscany&rdquo; and everybody smiles. Tuscany and her cuisine are incredibly loved and that&rsquo;s totally justified since the&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Toscani</span>&nbsp;cook dishes that represent the perfect combination of simplicity, purity and intensity.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="Standaard-P" style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong>For the TUSCANY 1 workshop</strong> we start with</span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong>two types of&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">crostini</span> </strong></span><strong>toscani</strong></span>. As main dishes we have</span><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">pici briciolati</span></strong><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">, thick hand-made spaghetti with garlic, chili peppers and crunchy breadcrumbs</span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">, plus&nbsp;<strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">scottiglia</span></strong>, a wonderful stew with vegetables, red wine and several types of meat together with<strong> two side dishes</strong></span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">. We end our meal with two sweet specialties, the<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;<strong>ricciarelli</strong></span> cookies from Siena and the&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">cantuccini</span></strong><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;from Prato (the famous almond cookies that we&rsquo;ll dip in&nbsp;</span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">vinsanto,&nbsp;</span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">THE Tuscan dessert wine).<br /><br /></span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><strong>In our TUSCANY 2*** workshop</strong></strong> we make <em>crostini di caccia toscani </em>(crostini with chicken liver pat&eacute;)<em>, testaroli al pesto etrusco</em> (handmade testaroli pasta with Etruscan pesto), <em>peposo </em>(a rich beef stew with vegetables, red wine and lots of black pepper), <em>funghi in umido alla toscana</em> (stewed mushrooms) and <em>torta della nonna</em> (a pie filled with custard and pine nuts).<br />All our dishes are &ldquo;supported&rdquo; by excellent Tuscan wines</span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">.</span></p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Dates TUSCANY 1: </span></strong><strong>Thursday 6 February 2014, Thursday April 3 2014</strong></p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Date TUSCANY 2: </span></strong><strong>Tuesday 21 January 2014</strong> <span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>(this workshop is held in the beautiful kitchen of cooking shop <a href="http://divine-delicious.web-interface.nl/" target="_blank">Kookwinkel Divine&amp;Delicious</a>)</strong></span></span><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Price:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; lin