(102, 214, 106, 'Napoli', '<h1 style="margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 30px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b72025; background-color: #fbaa3e;">The Neapolitan cuisine</h1>\n<p class="Standaard-P" style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">The Neapolitan way of cooking is full of authentic &ldquo;typically Italian&rdquo; tastes thanks to the use of classic ingredients such as tomato &ndash; lots of it! &ndash; mozzarella, pasta and fresh herbs.</span></p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">We&rsquo;re eating&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">mozzarella in carrozza</span></strong><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;(golden brown and crunchy fried&nbsp;</span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&ldquo;mozzarella sandwiches&rdquo;</span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;with sun-dried tomatoes and herbs),&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">maltagliati con le patate</span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">, a spicy&nbsp;<strong>home-made pasta</strong>&nbsp;with potatoes, red chili peppers and fresh herbs, and the famous&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">parmigiana di melanzane</span></strong><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">, a very rich oven dish with grilled&nbsp;</span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">aubergines</span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">, mozzarella and an intense tasting tomato-basil sauce.<br />As a dessert we make a&nbsp;</span><span class="Standaard-C23" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">torta caprese</span></strong>,</span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;a delicious cake&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="Standaard-C7" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">with almonds and chocolate. And of course we&rsquo;ll drink a glass of cold&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">limoncello</span></strong><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;with it.<br />With our meal we drink some of the intense wines from the region&nbsp;<strong>Campania</strong>.<br /></span></p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Dates:&nbsp;</span></strong><strong>&nbsp;Saturday 1 February, Wedne