(104, 214, 106, 'Pizza', '<h1 style="margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 30px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b72025; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Pizza, focaccia &amp; calzone workshop</h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">During this cookery workshop we prepare&nbsp;<strong>focaccia with rosemary and coarse sea salt</strong>&nbsp;plus several types of&nbsp;<strong>pizza</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>calzone</strong>&nbsp;using an original&nbsp;<strong>pizza stone</strong>. The ingredients may include grilled veggies, fresh mozzarella and other wonderful Italian cheeses, cherry tomatoes, arugula, green asparagus, ham, tuna, olives, capers, and much, much more!&nbsp;<br />After kneading our dough and making the pizzas we will of course eat everything accompanied by a few glasses of wine. It&rsquo;s going to be an unforgettable lunch!<br /><br />After the workshop you&rsquo;ll get a little &ldquo;starter package&rdquo; so that you can immediately make pizza at home.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Dates:&nbsp;</span></strong><strong>Saturday 1 March 2014</strong><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Price:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&euro; 79,00 p.p.</span><br /></strong></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Time:&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">10.30 to 14.30 hrs</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">To enroll please send an email through the "Contact" page.</span></strong></span></p>', '1f6a3e91725ce1c5d4effb1485584665.jpg', '', '01. 03. 2014.', 1, 11, 0, '2013-12-07 13:45:37'),
(105, 213, 106, 'Puglia', '<h1 style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia1, Georgia, serif; font-size: 30px; line-height: 160%; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b72025; background-color: #fbaa3e; font-weight: bold;">De keuken van Puglia</h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Puglia (Apulie) is de "hak" van Itali&euml; en de streek waar ik (Nicoletta) opgegroeid ben. Van mijn 8ste tot mijn 22ste heb ik daar gewoond en van de verrukkelijke lokale keuken (&eacute;&eacute;n van mijn favoriete regionale keukens) genoten. Een workshop over deze streek is dus een terechte "hommage" aan de regio die mij groot heeft gebracht.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">We beginnen met een&nbsp;<strong>calzone di cipolla</strong>&nbsp;(een heerlijke focaccia gevuld met zoete uiten, pecorino en olijven), dan volgt er een gerecht uit de Salento streek genoemd ciceri e tria (zelfgemaakte pasta met Primitivo wijn, kruiden, groenten en kikkererwten) en daarna gaan we een klassieker uit Bari, "hoofdstad" van Apuli&euml; te bereiden: de&nbsp;<strong>braciolette al sugo</strong>&nbsp;(kleine rundvleesrolletjes in tomatensaus, gevuld o.a. met knoflook, pecorinokaas en verse kruiden). De bijgerechten zijn eveneens bewerkelijk, spannend en smakelijk:&nbsp;<strong>peperoni ripieni</strong>&nbsp;(paprika''s gevuld met o.a. kappertjes en olijven uit de oven) en&nbsp;<strong>polpette di melanzane (</strong>gefrituurde aubergineballetjes met pecorino en oregano). En dan, dulcis in fundo, het toetje. De vruchtbare, donkerrode aarde van Apuli&euml; produceert fantastische vijgen. Daarom heb ik gekozen voor de&nbsp;<strong>fichi ripieni al cioccolato,</strong>&nbsp;zongedroogde vijgen in likeurwijn gevuld met amandelen en gedoopt in gesmolten chocola.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Data:</span>&nbsp; </span>donderdag 20 maart 2014, donderdag 30 oktober 2014</strong><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Prijs:</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;&euro; 79,00 p.p.</span><br /></strong></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Tijd:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">18.30 t/m 22.30 uur</span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span class="prijs" style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Om in te schrijven stuur ajb een mailtje via de "<a href="../../contact" target="_blank">Contact</a>" pagina.</span></strong></span></p>', 'd2a56536c61affc783bb9630f17f1689.jpg', '', '04. 02. 2014.', 1, 8, 1, '2013-12-07 13:49:26'),
(106, 214, 106, 'Puglia', '<h1 style="margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 30px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b72025; background-color: #fbaa3e;">The Apulian cuisine</h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Puglia is the &ldquo;heel&rdquo; of the boot (Italy) and the region where I (Nicoletta) grew up. I lived there from age 8 to age 22 and there I learned to enjoy the fantastic local cuisine, most probably my favourite in the whole of Italy. A workshop about this region is then a real &ldquo;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">hommage</span>&rdquo; to the area that formed me in many senses, especially the culinary one.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">We start with a&nbsp;<strong>calzone di cipolla</strong>, a wonderful focaccia filled with sweet onions, olives and pecorino, then we prepare a dish from the Salento area called&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">ciceri e tria</span>&nbsp;(<strong>handmade pasta with Primitivo wine</strong>, herbs, vegetables and chickpeas) to proceed with a classic from Bari, &ldquo;capital&rdquo; of Puglia: the<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">braciolette al sugo</span>&nbsp;(small&nbsp;<strong>beef rolls</strong>&nbsp;in tomato sauce filled with garlic and pecorino cheese). Also the side dishes are interesting:&nbsp;<strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">peperoni ripieni</span></strong>&nbsp;(filled bell peppers from the oven) and&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">polpette di melanzane</span>(<strong>aubergine fritters</strong>&nbsp;with pecorino and oregano). And then, dessert: stuffed dried&nbsp;<strong>figs marinated in liqueur&nbsp;</strong>and dipped in chocolate.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Dates:</span>&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span class="datetext" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Thursday </span></strong><strong>20 March 2014</strong><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Price:</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;&euro; 79,00 p.p.</span><br /></strong></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Time:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">on Wed. and Thu: 18.30 to 22.30, on Sun. 16.30 to 21.00 hrs</span></strong></span></p>', 'd2a56536c61affc783bb9630f17f1689.jpg', '', '20. 03. 2014.', 1, 9, 2, '2013-12-07 13:49:26');
