(108, 213, 106, 'Detoxen', '<h1 style="color: #b72025; font-size: 30px; font-family: Georgia1, Georgia, serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 160%;">Detoxen</h1>\n<p><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Nadat ik de bestseller "</span><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">In 28 dagen van gifbelt naar tempel</span></strong><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">" had gelezen en het 28-dagen </span><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">detoxprogramma</strong><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&nbsp;had gevolgd werd ik meteen een fan van&nbsp;</span><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Jacqueline van Lieshout</strong><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&nbsp;van <a href="http://www.detoxcoach.nl" target="_blank">www.detoxcoach.nl</a>. Wat een leuke vrouw! Enthousiast, gedreven &eacute;n heel goed in wat ze doet.</span> <span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Elkaar ontmoeten was de volgende stap en uit deze ontmoeting is er een&nbsp;</span><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">speciale detox-workshop </strong><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 1