px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&nbsp;van haar detox-programma.</span><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">We hebben veel gerechten op ons menu, van&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong>parmigiana di zucchine&nbsp;</strong></span><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">(courgette-ovenschotel) tot </span><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">risotto al limone</span></strong><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&nbsp;(met citroen), gepofte en gemarineerde paprika''s, pittige visfilets met paddenstoelen en courgette, een&nbsp;</span><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">frittata</span></strong><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&nbsp;met geroosterde groenten, een dessert en nog veel meer.</span><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">In totaal maken we&nbsp;</span><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">minstens 10 verschillende gerechten</strong><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&nbsp;en schenken we aandacht aan het bereiden van verse sappen en smoothies en aan alle belangrijke details die een&nbsp;</span><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">28-dagen detox</strong><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&nbsp;makkelijk &eacute;n lekker maken.&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Data:&nbsp;</span><span class="datetext" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">zaterdag 11 januari 2014 en zaterdag 15 februari 2014&nbsp;</span></strong><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Geor