(110, 213, 106, 'Italiaans koken zonder tarwe, koemelk en suiker', '<h1 style="margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 30px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b72025; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Workshop Italiaans koken zonder tarwe, koemelk en suiker</span></strong></h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Een workshop over de Italiaanse keuken, en dan</span>&nbsp;nog lichter, gezonder en bijzonderder dan deze keuken al kan zijn.<br /><br />Is het mogelijk om &eacute;cht Italiaans te koken zonder tarwepasta?<br />Natuurlijk! Nicoletta eet al jaren vaak tarwe- en koemelkvrij en heeft een heleboel heerlijke gerechten ontwikkeld die zeer geschikt zijn voor mensen die ook anders en toch heel lekker willen eten.&nbsp;<br /><br />Van glutenvrije pasta''s tot heerlijke hoofdgerechten, van pannenkoeken tot groenten en desserts, dit menu laat je ontdekken hoe makkelijk het eigenlijk is om "anders" Italiaans te koken en welke producten je kunt gebruiken om je streven naar een gezonder en toch heerlijk leven te steunen.<br /><br />Tijden deze workshop gebruiken we&nbsp;<strong>verschillende graansoorten</strong>&nbsp;(geen tarwe, wel af en toe granen die gluten bevatten) en&nbsp;<strong>kaas van geiten- en schapenmelk</strong>. Ook&nbsp;<strong>vlees</strong>&nbsp;- uitsluitend biologisch - staat op het menu. Als je&nbsp;<strong>vegetari</strong><strong>&euml;r</strong>&nbsp;bent, geen probleem, we hebben veel heerlijke vegetarische gerechten op het menu!<br /><br /><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Data:&nbsp;</span><span class="datetext" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">zaterdag 3 mei 2014</span></strong><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Prijs:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&euro; 79,00 p.p.</span></strong>&nbsp;<br /></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Tijden:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">10.30 uur t/m 14.30 uur<br /></span></strong></span><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Om in te schrijven stuur ajb een mailtje via de "<a href="../../contact" target="_blank">Contact</a>" pagina.</span></strong></span></p>', 'cab.jpg', '', '03. 05. 2014', 1, 10, 0, '2013-12-09 11:01:11'),
(112, 213, 106, 'Workshops met individuele inschrijving', '<h1 style="margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 30px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #fbaa3e; list-style-type: none; font-family: Georgia; line-height: 19px; color: #b72025;">Workshops met individuele inschrijving</h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #fbaa3e; list-style-type: none; font-family: Georgia; line-height: 19px; color: #000101;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: #ffa225; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none;"><span class="curs-text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: #ffffff; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: #000101; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;">(om meer tekst te zien klik op tekst en scroll naar beneden met PgDown of pijltje)</span><br /><br /></span></span></strong></span>Regelmatig organiseert La Cucina del Sole eenmalige kookworkshops (doordeweekse avonden 18:30-22.30 uur, zaterdagochtend om 10.30-14.30 uur en zondagmiddag 16.30-21.30) rond een specifieke Italiaanse kookthema.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #fbaa3e; list-style-type: none; font-family: Georgia; line-height: 19px; color: #000101;">Onze kookworkshop beginnen met een glas Prosecco en borrelhapjes (koffie/thee/sap met iets lekkers tijdens de ochtendsessies) om daarna verder te gaan met het te maken menu en aansluitend lunch of diner waar we samen alle bereide gerechten aan een mooi gedekte tafel nuttigen.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #fbaa3e; list-style-type: none; font-family: Georgia; line-height: 19px; color: #000101;">Een eenmalige kookworkshop met individuele inschrijving kost&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none;"><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;">&euro; 79,00 p.p.&nbsp;</span></strong></span><br />(<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none;"><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;">&euro; 89,00 p.p.&nbsp;</span></strong></span>voor het Kerst/Paasmenu) voor een les van ong. 4,5 uur met een Italiaans 3-gangen menu inclusief Prosecco, wijn, overige dranken, geprinte recepten en gebruik van schort van La Cucina del Sole. Je hoeft niet zelf af te wassen en schoon te maken, wij doen het wel!&nbsp;<br />Voor prijzen van kookworkshops met eigen groep kijk onder "Mogelijkheden".</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #fbaa3e; list-style-type: none; font-family: Georgia; line-height: 19px; color: #000101;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none;"><span class="specialtext" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: #ffffff; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;">Inschrijvingen:&nbsp;</span></strong></span>om een kookworkshop of kookcursus te boeken stuur ons ajb een mailtje (zie "Contact" op de site). Ook kun je een&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none;">cadeaubon</strong>&nbsp;kopen om een&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none;">workshop aan iemand cadeau</strong>&nbsp;te geven. Mail ons!<br />Italiaanse kookschool La Cucina del Sole behoudt zich het recht bij onvoldoende aanmeldingen de workshops/cursussen te annuleren. Vooruitbetaalde bedragen worden dan per bankrekening teruggestort of blijven geldig voor een volgende cursus/workshop.<br /><br />La Cucina del Sole&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-family: ''Bookman Old Style'', serif; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: 18px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;">&reg;</span>&nbsp;2002 - 2013</p>', '8ea8707afb9bfcb80dbaa4ee8751618f.jpg', '', '', 1, 2, 1, '2013-12-11 15:27:49'),
(113, 214, 106, 'Workshops with individual enrollment', '<h1 style="margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 30px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b72025; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Workshops with individual enrollment</h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #ffa225;"><strong><span class="curs-text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #ffffff;">(to see more text click on it and scroll down with PgDown or arrow)<br /></span></span></strong></span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">La Cucina del Sole&nbsp;</span>regularly&nbsp;</span><span class="Standaard-C7" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">organizes cooking classes&nbsp;</span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">on&nbsp;</span><span class="Standaard-C8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">specific Italian theme</span><span class="Standaard-C8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">s</span><span class="Standaard-C7" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;during the day or in the evenings&nbsp;</span><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">(on&nbsp;<strong>weekdays at 18.30</strong>, on&nbsp;<strong>Saturdays at 10.30</strong>&nbsp;and on&nbsp;<strong>Sundays at 16.30</strong>&nbsp;<strong>hrs</strong>)</span><span class="Standaard-C8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">. In this case,&nbsp;<strong>no group booking is compulsory</strong>, you can book just for yourself, for you and your partner/friend or for you and a couple more people.<br />A glass of Prosecco and nibbles in the evening or coffee/tea with something sweet are our way to start a culinary workshop. We always prepare all the dishes and then eat them&nbsp;</span><span class="Standaard-C8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><span class="Standaard-C8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">together,&nbsp;</span>accompanied by great Italian wines</span><span class="Standaard-C8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">.</span></p>\n<p class="Standaard-P0" style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">The&nbsp;<strong>prices of these workshops</strong>&nbsp;(<strong>&euro; 79,00</strong>&nbsp;for all general workshops and</span><strong><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;&euro;</span></strong><span class="Standaard-C6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong>&nbsp;89,00</strong>&nbsp;for the Christmas workshop)&nbsp;</span><span class="Standaard-C7" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">include Prosecco (for the afternoon/evening sessions), all wines and other non-alcoholic drinks &ndash; Italian mineral water, fruit juices, coffee/tea/herbal tea and handouts with printed recipes. These cookery workshops are meant for people who come singularly, without a own group. This means you&rsquo;ll cook with people you don&rsquo;t know: a wonderful way to make new friends!<br /><br /></span>Should you want to organize an&nbsp;<strong>exclusive cookery workshop with your own group</strong>&nbsp;of friends, family or colleagues, we can accommodate groups from a minimum of 8 to a maximum of 85 people.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span class="specialtext" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #ffffff;">Enrolling: </span></strong></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">to enroll for a cooking workshop or a cookery course please send an email using the "<a href="../../contact" target="_blank">Contact</a>" page</span></strong></span>.</p>\n<h4 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Italian cookery school La Cucina del Sole retains the right to cancel the workshops/courses if the minimum number of participants is not reached. Already paid participation fees will be paid back by bank account or will give you the right to participate in a successive course/workshop.</span></h4>', '8ea8707afb9bfcb80dbaa4ee8751618f.jpg', '', '', 1, 2, 1, '2013-12-11 15:27:49'),
(114, 213, 106, 'Team building', '<h1 style="margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 30px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #fbaa3e; list-style-type: none; font-family: Georgia; line-height: 19px; color: #b72025;">Teambuilding workshops</h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #fbaa3e; list-style-type: none; font-family: Georgia; line-height: 19px; color: #000101;">Deze zijn de eenmalige kookworkshops waarbij men een middag of avond bij La Cucina del Sole met een eigen groep (collega''s, klanten, relaties enz.) boekt. Er doen dus geen buitenstaanders mee.&nbsp;<br /><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;">Deze kooklessen zijn een uitstekende manier om aan het teambuilding van jouw groep te werken. Iedereen leert elkaar beter kennen door samen te werken aan de bereiding van een fantastische Italiaanse maaltijd. En natuurlijk door alles samen op te eten onder het genot van uitstekende Italiaanse wijnen!&nbsp;</span><br />3-gangenmenu (5 of meer gerechten in totaal) inclusief borrelhapjes tijdens het koken, ingredi&euml;nten, recepten om ook thuis te koken, gebruik van schorten en schoonmaak na de kooklessen, inclusief 1 glas Prosecco, 2 glazen wijn en onbeperkt overige non-alcoholische drankjes, koffie en thee. Extra alcoholische dranken worden apart berekend op basis van nacalculatie.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #fbaa3e; list-style-type: none; font-family: Georgia; line-height: 19px; color: #000101;">Voor drankenprijzen kijk onder "Mogelijkheden". Voor deze workshops hanteren we een minimum aantal van 8 deelnemers. Bij minder dan 8 personen is de totale prijs &euro; 632,00 plus de kosten van de eventueel extra genuttigde alcoholhoudende drankjes.&nbsp;<br />De begintijd van deze lessen kan vari&euml;ren tussen 16.30 en uiterlijk 19.00 uur.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #fbaa3e; list-style-type: none; font-family: Georgia; line-height: 19px; color: #000101;">Een kookworkshop duurt circa 4-4,5 uur.</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #fbaa3e; list-style-type: none; font-family: Georgia; line-height: 19px; color: #000101;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit;">Prijs:</span>&nbsp;&euro; 79,00 p.p. ex. BTW voor bedrijven, incl. BTW voor particulieren</strong></p>', '4e55be4b58e2d2683789f2b49e44224c.jpg', '', '', 1, 13, 1, '2013-12-11 15:29:31');
