(120, 214, 106, 'Detox', '<p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e; text-decoration: underline;"><strong>THIS WORKSHOP IS TAUGHT IN DUTCH.</strong></span><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">After I read the bestseller "</span><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">In 28 dagen van gifbelt naar tempel</span></strong><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">" and I did the&nbsp;</span><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">28-day detox program</strong><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&nbsp;I became a fan of&nbsp;</span><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Jacqueline van Lieshout</strong><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&nbsp;of www.detoxcoach.nl. What a nice, inspired and competent woman she is!</span><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Meeting each other was the next step and that get-together brought us to the idea of a&nbsp;</span><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">special detox workshop</strong><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">: detoxing the Italian way!</span><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Jacqueline will help us with all the&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;">ins &amp; outs</span><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&nbsp;of her detox program and I''ll take care of explaining the recipes and the preparation of a great detox meal!</span><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">We have many different dishes on our menu, from the&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong>parmigiana di zucchine&nbsp;</strong></span><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">(oven dish with courgette and tomato) to a nice</span><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">risotto al limone</span></strong><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&nbsp;(with lemon), roasted &amp; marinated belle peppers. spicy fish fillets with mushrooms and courgettes, a</span><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">frittata</span></strong><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&nbsp;with roasted veggies, a dessert and much more.</span><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">In total we''ll make&nbsp;</span><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">at least 10 different dishes.&nbsp;</strong><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">We will also prepare some fresh juices and smoothies with a slow juicer. It''s going to be a</span><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">&nbsp;great, easy and very tasty 28-day detox</strong><span style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">!&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Dates:&nbsp;</span><span class="datetext" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Saturday 11 of Januari 2014 (2 places left) and Saturday 15 of February 2014&nbsp;</span></strong><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Price:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&euro; 89,00 p.p.</span><br /><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Time:</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;10.30 t/m 14.30 uur<br /></span></strong></span><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">To enroll please send an email using the "<a href="../../contact" target="_blank">Contact</a>" page.</span></strong></span></p>', 'd511aea3ffbd54d1f037a734bdf2f133.jpg', '', '15. 02. 2014.', 0, 2, 1, '2013-12-12 12:37:35');
