(123, 214, 106, 'Cook without cow''s milk, wheat & sugar', '<h1 style="margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 30px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #b72025; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Workshop Italian cooking without wheat, cow''s milk and sugar</span></strong></h1>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">A workshop on the Italian cuisine, and then an even lighter one, healthier and even more special than Italian cooking already can be</span>.<br /><br />Is it really possible to cook real Italian food&nbsp; without wheat pasta?<br />Of course!&nbsp;<strong>Nicoletta</strong>&nbsp;of La Cucina del Sole has been experimenting for years with Italian cooking without wheat, cow''s milk and sugar and has developed a lot of wonderful recipes and techniques that are extremely usuful if you want to eat "different" and yet delicious Italian food.&nbsp;<br /><br />Learn how to make gluten-free pasta, wonderful main dishes, pancakes, side dishes and desserts. The menu will let you discover how easy and delicious a "different" way of Italian cooking can be and which products you can use to support a healthier and yet incredibly tasty way of life!<br /><br />During this workshop we use<strong>&nbsp;different types of grains&nbsp;</strong>(no wheat, and yet we do use grains that contain gluten like spelt) and<strong>&nbsp;cheese made with sheep''s and goats'' milk</strong>. Also<strong>&nbsp;meat&nbsp;</strong>- strictly organic - will be part of our menu. If you''re a&nbsp;<strong>vegetarian</strong>&nbsp;or prefer to avoid meat don''t worry, there will be plenty of alternatives for you!<br /><br /><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Dates:&nbsp;</span><span class="datetext" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Saturday 3 May</span></strong><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Price:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&euro; 79,00 p.p.</span></strong>&nbsp;<br /></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Hours:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">10.30 hrs - 14.30 hrs</span></strong></span></p>', 'cab.jpg', '', '03. 05. 2014.', 1, 12, 0, '2013-12-13 11:43:31'),
(124, 213, 106, 'Piemonte', '<p>Piemonte is de prachtige streek waar ik mijn eerste levensjaren heb doorgebracht en waar mijn liefde voor risotto is geboren!<br /><br />Tijdens deze Piemontese kookworkshop maken we <strong>crostini van polenta met geroosterde paprika''s</strong> in groene saus, <strong><em>gnocchi di patate al gorgonzola</em> </strong>(aardappelgnocchi in gorgonzolasaus), <strong>koolbladeren gevuld met een heerlijk gekruid gehakt</strong>, <em>funghi trifolati</em> (gebakken champignons), <em>tortino di patate e zucchine</em> (aardappel-courgettetaartje uit de oven) en <strong><em>bunet all''astigiana</em> </strong>(zachte puddinkjes met in rum geweekte rozijnen en veel chocola).<br /><br /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Datum: </span><span class="datetext" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">zondag 19 oktober</span> </strong><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Prijs:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: