(125, 214, 106, 'Piemonte', '<p>Piemonte is the beautiful region in which I spent the first part of my life. The great dishes from this area still represent one of the best memories of my childhood and it''s in Piemonte that my passion for risotto was born!<br /><br />During this Piemontese cooking workshop we prepare some nice polenta crostini with roasted bell peppers in green sauce, potato gnocchi in gorgonzola sauce, cabbage leaves filled with fragrant minced meat, <em>a tortino di patate e zucchine</em> (potato-courgette gratin), baked champignons and a moist <em>bonet all''astigiana</em>, a sweet pudding with raisins soaked in rum and lots of chocolate.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Our meal will be completed by some wonderful wines from Piemonte.<br /><br /><br /><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Date: </span></strong><strong style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;">Tuesday 18 February 2014</strong><br style="color: #000101; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #fbaa3e;" /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong>Price:&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&euro; 79,00 p.p.</span></strong>&nbsp;<br /></span><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; line-h