(127, 214, 106, 'The Roman cuisine', '<p>La Capitale, the capital, Roma... my favourite Italian city!</p>\n<p>Gorgeous, chaotic, straightforward and delicious. And her food is also fantastic: simple, nutricious and most of all very tasty!</p>\n<p><br />During this cookery workshop we prepare different typical dishes like the <strong>crostini romani</strong> with ham, mozzarella and champignons, <strong><em>quadrucci coi piselli</em> </strong>(home-made pasta with peas and pancetta), a creamy<strong><em>abbacchio alla romana</em> </strong>(lamb stew with lemon, saffron and egg), <strong>stuffed tomatoes </strong>bakedin the de oven and<strong> sweet ravioli</strong> filled with ricotta and chocolate.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000101; background-color: #fbaa3e;"><strong><span class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Date: </span><span class="datetext" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Tuesday 4 March</span> 2014</strong><br /><span class="prijs" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Price:</span>&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline